#. Tag: title
#: man-cvslastchange.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beskrivelse"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cvslastchange.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cvslastchange; displays the last change committed to &CVS; for a file. It "
"uses <command>cvs diff</command> and <command>cvs log</command> to do this."
msgstr ""
"&cvslastchange; viser den seneste ændring som er arkiveret i &CVS; for en "
"fil. Det bruger <command>cvs diff</command> og <command>cvs log</command> "
"til at gøre det."

#. Tag: para
#: man-cvslastchange.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "&cvslastchange; works on any &CVS; branch, not just HEAD."
msgstr "&cvslastchange; virker for alle &CVS;-grene, ikke kun HEAD."

#. Tag: para
#: man-cvslastchange.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "Værktøjet er en del af &kde;'s programmeludviklingsmiljø."

